  {
    "name": "JSONPlaceholder_get_post",
    "description": "Get a specific post by ID from JSONPlaceholder, a free fake REST API for testing and prototyping. Returns the post with userId, id, title, and body. Contains 100 posts total. No authentication required. Useful for testing API integrations, building prototypes, or learning REST API concepts.",
